(1, 1, '2015-07-13 19:22:45', '2015-07-13 18:22:45', '<strong>Cng ty TNHH KTM (KTM) - trc thuc trng Trung cp Kinh t - Ti nguyn v Mi trng c nhim v xy dng v trin khai cc chng trnh hp tc quc t, trong  c bit u tin tm kim c hi cho sinh vin tham gia cc chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lmv du hc nc ngoi.</strong>\r\n\r\nTham gia chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lm v du hc nc ngoil c hi tuyt vi cho cc bn tr nng cao ngoi ng, tch ly kin thc, kinh nghim, k nng lm vic v thu nhp, p ng yu cu ngun nhn lc cht lng cao trong thi k hi nhp Quc t su rng.\r\n\r\nCng ty TNHH KTM (KTM) - Trng trung cp Kinh t - Ti nguyn v Mi trng  thit lp quan h hp tc vi nhiu t chc Quc t v hin ang trin khai thnh cng nhiu chng trnh thc tp ngh, vic lm v du hc ti cc nc nh: Nht, M, Israel, Philipin, i Loan...Trong thi gian ti, trung tm s tip tc m rng nhng chng trnh ny sang cc nc khc nh c, Ailen, Hn Quc, Canada....', 'Qu trnh hnh thnh v pht trin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gioi-thieu-chung', '', '', '2015-09-25 05:52:34', '2015-09-25 03:52:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/demowp/wallbase/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
