(20, 1, '2015-07-14 20:19:59', '2015-07-14 19:19:59', '<strong>Trung tm o to v Pht trin quc t (ITC) trc thuc trng i hc Nng Lm  i hc Thi Nguyn c nhim v xy dng v trin khai cc chng trnh hp tc quc t, trong  c bit u tin tm kim c hi cho sinh vin tham gia cc chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lmv du hc nc ngoi.</strong>\r\n\r\nTham gia chng trnh Thc tp ngh nghip, vic lm v du hc nc ngoil c hi tuyt vi cho cc bn tr nng cao ngoi ng, tch ly kin thc, kinh nghim, k nng lm vic v thu nhp, p ng yu cu ngun nhn lc cht lng cao trong thi k hi nhp Quc t su rng.\r\n\r\nTrung tm o to v Pht trin Quc t - Trng i hc Nng lm Thi Nguyn thit lp quan h hp tc vi nhiu t chc Quc t v hin ang trin khai thnh cng nhiu chng trnh thc tp ngh, vic lm v du hc ti cc nc nh: Nht, M, Israel, Philipin, i Loan...Trong thi gian ti, trung tm s tip tc m rng nhng chng trnh ny sang cc nc khc nh c, Ailen, Hn Quc, Canada....', 'Qu trnh hnh thnh v pht trin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-14 20:19:59', '2015-07-14 19:19:59', '', 1, 'http://localhost/demowp/wallbase/2015/07/14/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
