(275, 11, '2015-09-15 04:08:35', '2015-09-15 02:08:35', '<h3>Hc sinh Nht Bn yu mn b ng phc bi n l mt phn ca tui tr.</h3>\r\n<div class="text-conent">\r\n\r\nNhng b qun o ng phc l du n kh phai nht trong i hc sinh. i vi cc hcsinh Nht Bn, ng phc i vi h khng ch n thun l qun o m n cn l vn ha, tng trng cho tui thanh xun. Ngi Nht rt yu mn vn ha ng phc ca h v th trang phcc bit ny cng quy t c mt lng fan ng o khp th gii, truyn cm hng cho nhiu thit k trang phc hc ng ti nhiu quc gia khc.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-0" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-0" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-1.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 1" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc n sinh Nht Bn</p>\r\n<em>Di y l tt c nhng iu bn cn bit v b ng phc ca Nht Bn</em>\r\n<h3><strong>1. Lch s ca b ng phc Nht Bn</strong></h3>\r\nng phc Nht Bn  c tui i ti 150 nm. N ln u tin c ra i vo thi Minh Tr vi mc ch l nhm xa b i khong cch giu ngho trong trng hc. Kiu ng phc u tin l mt b o s mi i km kimono v qun hakama (qun hakama l kiu qun ging vy xp np).\r\n\r\nSau , khi vn ha phng Ty du nhp, ng phc Nht Bn c nhiu s i khc. Hc sinh mc o khoc tn gi l Gakuran c phn c cao, ng v qun thy th mu xanh en hoc en ly cm hng t trang phc qun i Ph (Vo thi im  qun i Ph c xem l mnh nht th gii).\r\n\r\nB ng phc phong cch thy th ni ting ca x Ph Tang c ra i vo nm 1920. Ti nm 1980, o khoc blazer  b vo trng hc.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-1" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-1" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-2.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 2" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">B ng phc thy th ni ting</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-2" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-2" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441365220-34594051.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 3" width="500" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">ng phc nam sinh rt chn chu</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. Cc kiu ng phc n sinhph bin ti Nht</strong></h3>\r\nng phc n sinh Nht Bn gy c n tng p bis n tnh, trong sng, duyn dng. C rt nhiu kiu vy o ng phc. Mt s loi ph bin nh:\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-3" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-3" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-17.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 4" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc vy o kiu thy th</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-4" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-4" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-3.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 5" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc o blazer</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-5" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-5" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-4.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 6" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc o ngn bolero</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-6" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-6" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-5.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 7" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc lch thip theo phong cch trng Eton (Mt ngi trng ni ting chuyn o to chnh tr gia  Anh)</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-7" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-7" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-6.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 8" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc kiu vy ym</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-8" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-8" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-7.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 9" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc vy km dy eo qua vai</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-9" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-9" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-8.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 10" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ng phc vy lin</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. ng phc Nht c g?</strong></h3>\r\nng phc trng t v trng cng ca Nht Bn cng c nhiu s khc bit. ng phc trng t thng phc tp v nhiu mn ph kin hn trng cng. Tuy nhin ti mt s trng khng ph bin, hc sinh c th mc trang phc gn ging ng phc m h c th mua ti cc hng thi trang c dng hng c bit dnh cho gii tr. H c th chn vy v n nhiu mu khc nhau v phi chng kh thi trang. Mt s nhn hng Nht Bn cng tung ra cc sn phm c o c thit k ly  tng t ng phc.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-10" class="shareImage"></span><img id="news-image-id-10" class="news-image" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-9.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 11" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Nhiu nhn hng tung ra dng sn phm ging ng phc</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-11" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-11" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-10.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 12" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Vo ma ng, hc sinh thng mc cardigan, vest len</p>\r\nVo ma ng gi, hc sinh ti Nht thng mc o vest khng tay hoc carddigan len. Mu sc c bn thng l trng, en, xm, be.\r\n\r\ni tt m hc sinh Nht thng i cng thay i lin tc trong nhiu nm qua. Chng khng ch l tt  gi m chn ma ng m cn thay i tng th trang phc. i tt hc sinh ngy nay thng c chiu di ngay di u gi. Mt kiu tt khc cng kh ph bin l tt di 2/3 chiu di tnh t u gi n gt chn.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-12" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-12" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-12.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 13" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Tt thng thng</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-13" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-13" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-13.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 14" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">V tt thi trang</p>\r\nNgoi ra c mt kiu tt kh hay ho m n sinh Nht ang rt a chung l tt tr, xp nhn rt d thng.\r\n\r\nV giy, hc sinh Nht thng dng giy li, giy m ca  thp t 3  5 cm, lm t da. Mu sc thng l en v nu.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-14" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-14" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-14.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 15" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Giy m ca gt 3 phn</p>\r\nng phc n sinh Nht Bn khng th thiu nhng chic n xinh xn. Chng thng t khi b quy nh qu cht ch m vic chn la thng theo gu thi trang c nhn. Chn c chic n ng   phi cng ng phc kh th v.\r\n\r\nChiu di vy ca ng phc Nht Bn thng thng cao 15cm trn u gi. Vy n sinh x hoa anh o thng gy n tng v  ngn. N bt ngun t c th ca nc Nht l mt t nc chu nhiu thin tai, t ai nhiu ni kh cn, khng thch hp cho vic trng trt. Xa kia bng si l th rt him hoi v th trang phc dt t nhiu si l th rt t .\r\n\r\nNgi Nht t thi Edo thng mc  ngn  tit kim vi. Ngay c cc chin binh samurai trong mt s nghi l cng mc o gip cng qun cc. Ngy nay, nh s chu thng chu kh v bng ngh lc tuyt vi, nc Nht  tr thnh mt trong nhng cng quc hng u th gii. Ngnh cng nghip dt may x mt tri mc pht trin mnh m, vi si chc chn khng cn l mt th him hoi na nhng hc sinh Nht vn gi thi quen t thi ng cha, h vn thng mc qun, vy ngn ti trng.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-15" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-15" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384136-1441364813-15.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 16" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Vy ca n sinh Nht thng ngn trn u gi</p>\r\nMc d vy ngn bt ngun t truyn thng xa nhng n cng em li cho hc sinh nhiu phin toi. D i tt, nhng vo thi tit but gi ti Nht vo ma ng, chic vy ngn vn em ti nguy c v cn bnh thp khp. Ngoi ra khi ma gi, l lt, chic vy ngn cng gy ra khng t tnh hung t nh cho cc c gi tr.\r\n\r\nHc sinh Nht rt yu qu b ng phc ca h. Khng ch mc chng n trng hc, h thm ch cn mc khi khng ln lp, khi i chi, t tp bn b. Theo mt bi bo ca New York Time, hc sinh Nht cm thy t ho khi khoc ln ngi b ng phc v coi n nh mt biu tng ca tui tr.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-16" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-16" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384136-1441364813-16.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 17" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-3" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-3" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-17.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 4" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Ngi Nht rt yu mn b ng phc</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="nguontin" style="text-align: right;">Theo Thu Hng (danviet.vn)</div>', 'Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kham-pha-moi-dieu-ve-dong-ph