""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-11" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-10.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 12" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Vo ma ng, hc sinh thng mc cardigan, vest len</p>\r\nVo ma ng gi, hc sinh ti Nht thng mc o vest khng tay hoc carddigan len. Mu sc c bn thng l trng, en, xm, be.\r\n\r\ni tt m hc sinh Nht thng i cng thay i lin tc trong nhiu nm qua. Chng khng ch l tt  gi m chn ma ng m cn thay i tng th trang phc. i tt hc sinh ngy nay thng c chiu di ngay di u gi. Mt kiu tt khc cng kh ph bin l tt di 2/3 chiu di tnh t u gi n gt chn.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-12" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-12" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-12.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 13" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Tt thng thng</p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-13" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-13" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-13.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 14" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">V tt thi trang</p>\r\nNgoi ra c mt kiu tt kh hay ho m n sinh Nht ang rt a chung l tt tr, xp nhn rt d thng.\r\n\r\nV giy, hc sinh Nht thng dng giy li, giy m ca  thp t 3  5 cm, lm t da. Mu sc thng l en v nu.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-14" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-14" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-14.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 15" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Giy m ca gt 3 phn</p>\r\nng phc n sinh Nht Bn khng th thiu nhng chic n xinh xn. Chng thng t khi b quy nh qu cht ch m vic chn la thng theo gu thi trang c nhn. Chn c chic n ng   phi cng ng phc kh th v.\r\n\r\nChiu di vy ca ng phc Nht Bn thng thng cao 15cm trn u gi. Vy n sinh x hoa anh o thng gy n tng v  ngn. N bt ngun t c th ca nc Nht l mt t nc chu nhiu thin tai, t ai nhiu ni kh cn, khng thch hp cho vic trng trt. Xa kia bng si l th rt him hoi v th trang phc dt t nhiu si l th rt t .\r\n\r\nNgi Nht t thi Edo thng mc  ngn  tit kim vi. Ngay c cc chin binh samurai trong mt s nghi l cng mc o gip cng qun cc. Ngy nay, nh s chu thng chu kh v bng ngh lc tuyt vi, nc Nht  tr thnh mt trong nhng cng quc hng u th gii. Ngnh cng nghip dt may x mt tri mc pht trin mnh m, vi si chc chn khng cn l mt th him hoi na nhng hc sinh Nht vn gi thi quen t thi ng cha, h vn thng mc qun, vy ngn ti trng.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-15" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-15" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384136-1441364813-15.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 16" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Vy ca n sinh Nht thng ngn trn u gi</p>\r\nMc d vy ngn bt ngun t truyn thng xa nhng n cng em li cho hc sinh nhiu phin toi. D i tt, nhng vo thi tit but gi ti Nht vo ma ng, chic vy ngn vn em ti nguy c v cn bnh thp khp. Ngoi ra khi ma gi, l lt, chic vy ngn cng gy ra khng t tnh hung t nh cho cc c gi tr.\r\n\r\nHc sinh Nht rt yu qu b ng phc ca h. Khng ch mc chng n trng hc, h thm ch cn mc khi khng ln lp, khi i chi, t tp bn b. Theo mt bi bo ca New York Time, hc sinh Nht cm thy t ho khi khoc ln ngi b ng phc v coi n nh mt biu tng ca tui tr.\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-16" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-16" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384136-1441364813-16.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 17" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center"><span class="img-share"><span id="shareImage-3" class="shareImage"><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-fb.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /><span title=""><img src="http://24h-static.24hstatic.com/images/2014/share-gg.gif" alt="" width="67" height="20" /></span></span><img id="news-image-id-3" class="news-image aligncenter" src="http://24h-img.24hstatic.com/upload/3-2015/images/2015-09-04/1441384135-1441364813-17.jpg" alt="Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn - 4" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="center">Ngi Nht rt yu mn b ng phc</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="nguontin" style="text-align: right;">Theo Thu Hng (danviet.vn)</div>', 'Khm ph mi iu v ng phc hc sinh Nht Bn', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '275-revision-v1', '', ''