(342, 11, '2015-09-24 06:28:53', '2015-09-24 04:28:53', '<img class="irc_mi alignleft" src="http://duhoc.viet-sse.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Viec-lam-tai-nhat-1.jpg" alt="" width="304" height="184" />Ngi Vit Nam i Nht hc tp (du hc), i lao ng (tu nghip, thc tp sinh) u mong mun tm vic lm thm ngoi gi  tng thm thu nhp. c bit hin nay cc bn i kim tin (i lao ng) bng con ng i du hc th vic kim tin ngoi gi l ct li. Vy lm th no  c th tm c nhiu vic, kim c nhiu tin?\n<div>Ngi Nht ght nht tr trm cp. Cc bn du hc sinh cn dp b ngay  ngh tiu cc kiu nh " v tu", chm  siu th... Nu bn vi phm php lut th c th b ui v nc bt c lc no.</div>\n<div>Cch kim tin  Nht Bn</div>\n<div>Ti l ngi  i du hc t tc ti Nht, c thi gian sng, hc tp v lm vic  Nht khong 8 nm. Ti c c bi vit "V mng kim 30 triu ng mt thng khi du hc Nht" ca bn T Thy Lan v c nhng  kin bnh lun khc ca c gi.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Theo ti, gi khng phi l lc ngi trch c cng ty t vn du hc mc d "cc cng ty du hc, mi gii thn nhin v ra "tng lai mu hng" nh bn ni l nguyn nhn chnh dn n tnh cnh kh khn ca cc bn hin nay.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Theo ti, vic lm thit thc nht hin nay l:</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>1.</strong> Cc bn cha c vic lm nn thi gian rnh ri cn nhiu, gi l lc bn cn dnh ton b thi gian v sc lc  hc tp ting Nht. Ti bit iu ny khng d, nhng cc bn cn hiu rng cc bn ch c th tm c vic lm thm ti Nht nu c kh nng nghe, ni ting Nht tng i tt. Do , cn cp tc nng cao nng lc ting Nht ca bn trong thi gian cng ngn cng tt.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>2.</strong> Cn trao i mt cch thng thn v trung thc tnh hnh hin ti ca cc bn vi nh trng ni cc bn ang theo hc  h c phng n h tr: v d nh t chc dy thm ting Nht cp tc, cho chm np hc ph, tin nh, gii thiu vic lm thm, bi dng cch vit n xin vic, k nng d phng vn xin vic... Cc bn cn c c s cm thng v tin cy ca ngi Nht th mi c th ng vng  t nc mt tri mc.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>3.</strong> Tm thi qun i khon vay cho bn i du hc ca gia nh  Vit Nam, hy tranh th cc mi quan h ca mnh  Nht v ci chnh l da trn kh nng ca chnh mnh  sm tm c cng vic lm thm, trc ht vi mc ch m bo chi ph ti thiu ca bn  Nht. ng vi ngh ti vic tr n  Vit Nam hay lm giu...</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Khi bn c vic lm tt, c hc vn th bn s thc hin nhng mc tiu y sau.</div>\n<div>Ti ngh rng trn y l 3 gii php c bn.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Cui cng ch mun nhc bn mt iu: ngi Nht ght nht tr trm cp. Do vy cc bn cn dp b ngay  ngh tiu cc kiu nh " v tu", "chm  siu th"... Nu bn vi phm php lut th c th b ui v nc bt c lc no. Nu chuyn  xy ra th bn v gia nh s mt tt c. ng cha ta c cu "c ch th nn", tng lai ca bn vn ang trong tay bn .</div>\n<div>Ngun VNE</div>\n<div>@Nht Bn tng hp</div>', 'Cch tm vic, kim tin ti Nht Bn', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '231-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 06:28:53', '2015-09-24 04:28:53', '', 231, 'http://thuctapsinhktm.vn/2015/09/24/231-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
